# Version 1.11 compiles fine but installs
# shared libraries without the .so
# Therefore, the shared libraries installed by libdnet are unusable.

   version stable 1.11
  optional Python --with-python '' to create libdnet Python module
      opts --exec-prefix= --enable-static=no
  category network
 attribute library
 attribute broke
    source $SOURCEFORGE_URL libdnet/libdnet/libdnet-$VERSION/libdnet-$VERSION.tar.gz
      info home  http://libdnet.sourceforge.net/
      info mail  'http://sourceforge.net/mail/?group_id=36243'
      desc 'library to networking routes

libdnet provides a simplified, portable interface
to several low-level networking routines, including:

network address manipulation
kernel arp(4) cache and route(4) table lookup and manipulation
network firewalling (IP filter, ipfw, ipchains, pf, PktFilter, ...)
network interface lookup and manipulation
IP tunnelling (BSD/Linux tun, Universal TUN/TAP device)
raw IP packet and Ethernet frame transmission '

